Install g++ version 7
---------------------
$ sudo apt install libcurl4-nss-dev g++-7
$ sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/g++ g++ /usr/bin/g++-7 10

Then test that `g++ --version` shows the correct version number


Install curlpp library
----------------------
git clone https://github.com/jpbarrette/curlpp
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr . && make && sudo make install


Clone my starter code
---------------------
git clone https://bitbucket.org/erikfalor/Fa17-cs1440-hw7
cd Fa17-cs1440-hw7
make

                                
